title: Dear Victims @ KISS Expo Finland -98 with Eric Singer
description:
20:38 1.4.2008 - taukka

Dear Victims @ Tavastia / KISS Expo Helsinki &#039;98 with Eric Singer 12.5.1998


Man, this was a night to remember! We were asked if we&#039;d come and play in this KISS Expo, we said okay and the next thing I remember that T. Putaansuu called me and said that "...you&#039;re not gonna believe who&#039;s gonna come to the Expo as well...Eric Singer and guess what, you&#039;re gonna play on that same stage with him!".

Here&#039;s 1h 23min excerpt from that night. I had to cut several clips away, even from this short clip as there were some people that don&#039;t want to be seen nowadays without masks, that is! I don&#039;t wanna see their lawyers anywhere near us and of course, the guys & a girl want to remain anonymous, so I will grant them that and I will not show any of them in this video.

PLS NOTE!!!! After encoding, I noticed that there were some audio/video clippings in this *.avi, but I will make a better release soon as I&#039;ve heard that some of us has better quality material than I have. So bear with me!!!
